1
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:33,800
Ruirui

2
00:01:35,920 --> 00:01:37,040
They hit you again.

3
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:40,280
I can't take it anymore.

4
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:42,160
What are you doing?

5
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:44,240
I want to run away.

6
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:46,080
But when I got here,

7
00:01:46,520 --> 00:01:47,840
I thought about just jumping down.

8
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:49,360
Come on, come home with me.

9
00:01:53,600 --> 00:01:55,560
Every time my little brother cries, it's always my fault.

10
00:01:55,760 --> 00:01:57,760
Today I couldn't help but talk back to him a little.

11
00:01:57,760 --> 00:01:59,400
That man burned me with an iron.

12
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:01,920
My mom just stood there and watched.

13
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:04,840
The three of them are the real family.

14
00:02:08,120 --> 00:02:09,080
If you're tired,

15
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:10,600
