17
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:17,320
As long as you want.

18
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:20,680
Come on, come home with me.

19
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:08,600
Sister

20
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:12,560
Why are you up?

21
00:03:13,200 --> 00:03:14,000
Sister

22
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:16,920
Could you get me a glass of water?

23
00:03:17,320 --> 00:03:19,120
