26
00:03:25,320 --> 00:03:26,960
Alright, I'll go get some water.

27
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:28,000
Lie down quickly.

28
00:03:28,440 --> 00:03:29,400
Thank you.

29
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:26,720
Ning Ruirui

30
00:05:28,960 --> 00:05:29,480
Don't

31
00:05:29,960 --> 00:05:30,680
Don't move

32
00:05:30,680 --> 00:05:31,120
Be careful

33
